name: Christian Louboutin Replica Miss Cristo Leather Platform Wedges
description: Christian Loubutin replica Miss Critso strappy platform wedge. Dark brown leather uppers with bow detail on vamp. Cork Platform Wedge. Leather inner and outer soles. Signature red soles. Made in Spain. Size 37. Comes with original dustbag. New without box.

name: Bruno Magli "Arianna" Clear Vinyl and Black Satin Cap Toe Pumps
description: Bruno Magli vintage pumps. Made in Italy. Clear transparent vinyl and black satin uppers. Leather insoles and soles. Size 8 B in good condition. No tears, scrapes, stains or discolorations to the satin. The vinyl has some minimal wear from being used but nothing that is hardly noticeable when on. They do come with the original box, paper, and dustbag. Originally purchased from Neiman Marcus for $225.00.

name: Alessandro Dell'Acqua Black Leather Kitten Heel Slides
description: Alessandro Dell'Acqua kitten heel peeptoe slides. Made in Italy. Black leather uppers with small gold medallion on center of upper vamp. Leather insoles and soles. Size 39 in excellent almost new condition. Hardly any wear to soles due to only being used indoors on carpet. These do not come with original box or dustbag. These retailed for over $500.00 dollars.

name: Rafe New York Gold Leather and Tapestry Embellished Slides
description: Rafe New York kitten heel peeptoe slides. Made in Italy. Gold leather uppers with tapestry fabric. Leather insoles and soles. name: Douglas Hannant Green Tweed and Suede Cap Toe Pumps
description: Douglas Hannant new never used pumps. Made in Italy. Tweed green fabric and green suede uppers. Leather insoles and soles. Size 40 and in excellent condition. Retailed for over $700.00 dollars.
